      <!--Aboutme Starting-->

      <div class="container animate__animated animate__lightSpeedInLeft">  
       <div class="container nav-cont animate__animated animate__lightSpeedInLeft">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-3"><hr></div>
          <div class="col-sm-2"><a href="#vizyon">Vision</a></div>
          <div class="col-sm-2"><a href="#misyon">Mission</a></div>
          <div class="col-sm-2"><a href="#tarihçe">History</a></div>
          <div class="col-sm-3"><hr></div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
        <div class="container animate__animated animate__lightSpeedInLeft">
            <div class="row">
            <div class="bookworldfoto">
                <img src="/media/bookworld.png" alt="historyBookWorld" id="historyphoto">

            </div>
        </div>
          <div class="row">
            <section class="about py-5 mt-3">
                    <div class="container">
                      <h3 id="vizyon">Vision</h3><hr>
                      <p  class="aboutp">The vision of BookWorld is to make knowledge and education easily accessible, spread the culture of reading across the globe, and provide an inspiring learning platform for individuals of all ages. With this goal in mind, we aim to make information more accessible in the digital age, offering books and educational resources that support personal development. BookWorld is committed to developing its platform worldwide to not only provide books but also offer access to educational materials, articles, and journals. By leveraging technology and innovative solutions, we aspire to redefine the learning and discovery process, becoming a global educational resource.</p>
                      <p class="aboutp">We aim to make books and educational materials more accessible and useful, catering to people's hunger for knowledge and fostering reading habits. In the future, BookWorld will transform from merely a book platform into a global educational source that inspires and educates communities worldwide, driving a learning movement powered by technology and interactive content.</p></p>
                    </div>
                    
          </div>
          <div class="row">
          </section>
          <section class="about" class="py-5">
            <div class="container">
                <h3 id="misyon">Mission</h3><hr>
                <p class="aboutp">The mission of BookWorld is to provide easy access to knowledge for every individual, enabling them to quickly access books and educational content. We aim to popularize the culture of reading and make education accessible at every stage of life. On our platform, we offer thousands of books, articles, videos, and educational resources that cater to a wide range of age groups, interests, and educational levels, meeting every kind of learning need.</p>
                <p class="aboutp">BookWorld aims not only to entertain but also to inspire and support personal development through high-quality content. By organizing books and other educational resources in an effective manner, we provide a space where people can explore, learn, and reach their personal goals. Helping each individual discover and develop their potential in the learning process is our top priority.</p>
                <p class="aboutp"> Additionally, BookWorld seeks to make education more equitable. Our mission is to ensure that everyone, regardless of age or region, has access to educational resources, creating equal opportunities for learning through digital content and resources.</p>
                
            </div>
          </section>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
          </section>
          <section class="about" class="py-5">
            <div class="container">
                <h3 id="tarihçe">History</h3><hr>
                <p  class="aboutp">BookWorld was founded in 2024 with the goal of making books easily accessible to individuals worldwide. Initially launched as an online book-sharing platform, it has since evolved into a rich educational resource that includes books, e-books, articles, and learning materials. Our goal is to continuously expand the variety of content and offer a user-friendly platform that promotes reading habits and provides access to educational resources.</p>
            </div>
          </section>
          </div>
        </div>
     
     
